Class MainActivity

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      org.mobilesynergies.android.epic.service.core.MainActivity

public class MainActivity
extends Activity

Main entry point for the user. Shows status of the service and allows to start and stop the service. Allows the user to start the LoginActivity and the ServiceConfigurationActivity
